[
    {
        "text": "Watch that posture!",
        "startTime": 7175,
        "endTime": 8167,
        "slowStartTime": 10912,
        "slowEndTime": 12476
    },
    {
        "text": "When it comes to first impressions, your body language goes a long way...",
        "startTime": 8437,
        "endTime": 11755,
        "slowStartTime": 12805,
        "slowEndTime": 17858
    },
    {
        "text": "...in conveying confidence and competence.",
        "startTime": 11881,
        "endTime": 13923,
        "slowStartTime": 17972,
        "slowEndTime": 21109
    },
    {
        "text": "Learning how to carry yourself during a job interview...",
        "startTime": 14449,
        "endTime": 16803,
        "slowStartTime": 21823,
        "slowEndTime": 25429
    },
    {
        "text": "...may mean the difference between being written off and being remembered.",
        "startTime": 16898,
        "endTime": 20376,
        "slowStartTime": 25497,
        "slowEndTime": 30789
    },
    {
        "text": "You will need a strong walk, a firm grip, a connection and clarity.",
        "startTime": 22274,
        "endTime": 27841,
        "slowStartTime": 33561,
        "slowEndTime": 41986
    },
    {
        "text": "Step one. Walk in, make eye contact and deliver a handshake with a firm grip,...",
        "startTime": 28641,
        "endTime": 33969,
        "slowStartTime": 43111,
        "slowEndTime": 51179
    },
    {
        "text": "...looking your interviewer right in the eye.",
        "startTime": 34220,
        "endTime": 36070,
        "slowStartTime": 51480,
        "slowEndTime": 54330
    },
    {
        "text": "Confident body language suggests you are the perfect candidate for the job.",
        "startTime": 36536,
        "endTime": 39864,
        "slowStartTime": 54954,
        "slowEndTime": 60021
    },
    {
        "text": "Step two. Sit up straight with your feet firmly on the floor.",
        "startTime": 40827,
        "endTime": 44497,
        "slowStartTime": 61390,
        "slowEndTime": 66971
    },
    {
        "text": "Don't rock, drum fingers, glance around or shake your foot.",
        "startTime": 44801,
        "endTime": 48254,
        "slowStartTime": 67352,
        "slowEndTime": 72606
    },
    {
        "text": "Slumping, fidgeting or apparent impatience comes off as low self-esteem, or worse, disinterest.",
        "startTime": 48625,
        "endTime": 54375,
        "slowStartTime": 73088,
        "slowEndTime": 81787
    },
    {
        "text": "Step three. Connect with your interviewer.",
        "startTime": 55222,
        "endTime": 57750,
        "slowStartTime": 82983,
        "slowEndTime": 86850
    },
    {
        "text": "Nod, use your hands while talking and be enthusiastic...",
        "startTime": 58046,
        "endTime": 61380,
        "slowStartTime": 87219,
        "slowEndTime": 92295
    },
    {
        "text": "...without overdoing it to the point of distraction or insincerity.",
        "startTime": 61473,
        "endTime": 64966,
        "slowStartTime": 92360,
        "slowEndTime": 97674
    },
    {
        "text": "Step four. Enunciate clearly, taking time to consider questions.",
        "startTime": 65927,
        "endTime": 70740,
        "slowStartTime": 99041,
        "slowEndTime": 106335
    },
    {
        "text": "Convey the sincerity they can expect you to bring to the job.",
        "startTime": 71147,
        "endTime": 74176,
        "slowStartTime": 106871,
        "slowEndTime": 111489
    },
    {
        "text": "Speak slowly, deliberately, with resonance and confidence.",
        "startTime": 74568,
        "endTime": 78636,
        "slowStartTime": 112002,
        "slowEndTime": 118179
    },
    {
        "text": "Step five. Smile once in a while.",
        "startTime": 79615,
        "endTime": 82293,
        "slowStartTime": 119573,
        "slowEndTime": 123664
    },
    {
        "text": "Be personable and feel free to ask questions,...",
        "startTime": 82534,
        "endTime": 85076,
        "slowStartTime": 123951,
        "slowEndTime": 127839
    },
    {
        "text": "...taking control so that the interview becomes a relaxed conversation.",
        "startTime": 85292,
        "endTime": 88818,
        "slowStartTime": 128088,
        "slowEndTime": 133452
    },
    {
        "text": "Mirror the interviewer's body language, which is known as a joining technique.",
        "startTime": 89457,
        "endTime": 93368,
        "slowStartTime": 134336,
        "slowEndTime": 140277
    },
    {
        "text": "If their arms and/or legs are crossed or closed, do the same.",
        "startTime": 93538,
        "endTime": 96993,
        "slowStartTime": 140457,
        "slowEndTime": 145715
    },
    {
        "text": "If they move their hands when they speak, they're considered open.",
        "startTime": 97299,
        "endTime": 100341,
        "slowStartTime": 146099,
        "slowEndTime": 150737
    },
    {
        "text": "Step six. Walk out with purpose and strength.",
        "startTime": 101437,
        "endTime": 104819,
        "slowStartTime": 152305,
        "slowEndTime": 157453
    },
    {
        "text": "No matter how you feel you've done, leave with your head held high.",
        "startTime": 105071,
        "endTime": 108807,
        "slowStartTime": 157756,
        "slowEndTime": 163435
    },
    {
        "text": "Did you know?",
        "startTime": 110365,
        "endTime": 111010,
        "slowStartTime": 165697,
        "slowEndTime": 166740
    },
    {
        "text": "From 2006 through 2008, the number of Americans...",
        "startTime": 111466,
        "endTime": 115022,
        "slowStartTime": 167349,
        "slowEndTime": 172758
    },
    {
        "text": "...receiving outplacement support after a layoff increased by 50 percent.",
        "startTime": 115113,
        "endTime": 119796,
        "slowStartTime": 172820,
        "slowEndTime": 179919
    }
]